short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Defending your wallet from impulsive domain purchases.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Domain Goalie tries to stop you from purchasing new domains. When you go to checkout on one of the supported websites a popup will prompt you to confirm your intentions. You can either confirm to continue purchasing, or give in and let Domain Goalie clear your cart for you.

Supported websites:
* godaddy.com
* namecheap.com
* domains.google.com
* porkbun.com
* sav.com
* dynadot.com

To request a new supported website, report a bug, or request new features go to our website https://domaingoalie.com/.
